item.title: 5 Misconceptions About Pain Relief
item.description: Pain Relief Myth 1: No Pain, No Gain. Pain Relief Myth 2: It's All In My Head. Pain Relief Myth 3: I Just Have to Live with the Pain. Pain Relief Myth 4: Only Sissies Go to the Doctor for Pain Relief. Pain Relief Myth 5: Pain Medication Will Fix the Problem Great strides have been made in the understanding of pain and its treatment in the last decade. Pain that was once considered hopeless is now manageable.
